    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《极夜》（Kaamos）是一款轻量的回合制解谜类肉鸽游戏，你将在一个可以循环滚动的网格上，通过匹配图块来展开策略战斗。击败敌人，掠夺装备，逐步打造属于自己的角色和图块卡组。穿越这片永无黎明的中世纪黑暗世界，在无尽长夜中寻找出路。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/5f274f33a5109aad1b275b76f0dd98e6.poster.avif?t=1762917428\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/5f274f33a5109aad1b275b76f0dd98e6.webm?t=1762917428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/5f274f33a5109aad1b275b76f0dd98e6.mp4?t=1762917428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>回合制解谜战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在生死决斗中迎战敌人，提前预知他们的行动。通过拖动网格、匹配图块，以绝妙操作反制攻势。用刺击、重击与劈砍杀出一条胜路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/799539b0918c4c4cfa124dfa2c73b70a.poster.avif?t=1762917428\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/799539b0918c4c4cfa124dfa2c73b70a.webm?t=1762917428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/799539b0918c4c4cfa124dfa2c73b70a.mp4?t=1762917428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造你的角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >装备强力的武器、护甲与戒指，改变你的战术与图块搭配。你想成为双持狂战士、灵巧的决斗高手，还是身披重甲的骑士？游戏内超180件装备为你提供丰富的构筑路径和多样化战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/50358355e00daf6360eb97f7f766580f.poster.avif?t=1762917428\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/50358355e00daf6360eb97f7f766580f.webm?t=1762917428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/50358355e00daf6360eb97f7f766580f.mp4?t=1762917428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >穿越无日之地</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿行于随机生成的黑暗中世纪世界，疯狂潜伏其间。揭开太阳消失之谜，或在黑暗中沉沦。你并不孤单——每一个岔路口的阴影中，总有某种东西在等待。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/4285c84eaac0e52a4c55325fcbf3402d.poster.avif?t=1762917428\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/4285c84eaac0e52a4c55325fcbf3402d.webm?t=1762917428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3317660/extras/4285c84eaac0e52a4c55325fcbf3402d.mp4?t=1762917428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>温馨提示：本游戏目前仅支持英文版本。</i></p>",
